title: Cannabis Collection - Sea of Green all 4 volumes
description:
Here is a nice addition to the Cannabis Collection. All and everything that you ever wanted or needed to know about growing Cannabis, nicely explained by expert growers. All 4 volumes on dvd.

The Cannabis Collection - a series of educative and entertaining info dvd's
Check out this awesome Cannabis Collection - there are currently still more than 50 dvds available for download.
Please enjoy, share with friends and seed :)


Sea of Green - Vol. 1 - How to Flower Cannabis Clones

Invented in Holland and perfected in America, the "Sea of Green" technique places rooted clones into immediate flowering. It is the most effecient and productive means of cannabis cultivation.
Sea of Green is a very detailed instructional tape explaining the "Sea of Green" cultivation technique, which has been called the fastest and easiest growing process ever. This DVD illustrates the entire technique from seed to clone to speedy harvest.

Sea of Green - Vol. 2 - Closet Cultivation

Sea of Green, Vol. II: Closet Cultivation is part two of a three-volume instructional series on marijuana cultivation. The 60-minute video is a step-by-step guide that shows how to turn a closet or attic into a growing room that will produce 12 to 18 inch buds every two weeks. Topics covered in this "beginner's guide" include germination, cloning, lighting, and harvesting.

Sea of Green - Vol. 3 - Hydroponic Cultivation
See, the only Hydroponics video in the world. The "Ebb and Flow technique, has been adapted to the Sea of Green method. Special "wick method" process allows nutrient free, final harvest for that much sought after "chemical free" smoke, which most other processes do not have. Mother plant care, cloning, light, air, water, pumps, pH., PPM, transplanting, man made mediums, etc. all you need to know to become an expert hydroponics grower. This process has simplified hydroponics, and is an excellent video, to help eliminate those "beginner mistakes".

Sea of Green - Vol. 4 - Growing Sensemilla Marijuana

A must see for any novice or serious grower.
See...newest, scientifically designed, straight forward, visual presentation...unique growing process turns your closet or any unused space into a virtual gold mine. See...harvest unlimited amounts of 20 inch single stalk buds once every two weeks...self perpetuating...fastest, easiest growing process ever. See...easy to follow, no fail video...de-mystifies growing...learn the experts' secrets...from seed to clone to harvest.




Check this account for updates regularly :)

Thanks to the peers all over the globe seeding in this collection
